---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="About — Amplified Event Strategy"
  description="Founded in 2015, Amplified Event Strategy is a full-service crypto events agency behind 100+ flagship conferences including CoinDesk Consensus, Solana Breakpoint, Nearcon, and the Ondo Summit."
  bodyClass="inner-page">
  <header class="container-fluid header">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col">
        <div class="lg-text">
          <span>WE PRODUCE EVENTS</span><br />
          <span>THAT MOVE THE</span><br />
          <span>CRYPTO WORLD.</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="header-stats-outer">
      <div class="header-stats">
        <div class="header-stats-track">
          <div class="header-stat">
            <span class="stat-number">100+</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Events Produced</span>
          </div>
          <div class="header-stat">
            <span class="stat-number">10+</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Years in Crypto</span>
          </div>
          <div class="header-stat">
            <span class="stat-number">Global</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Reach</span>
          </div>
          <div class="header-stat">
            <span class="stat-number">Since 2015</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Industry Leaders</span>
          </div>
          <div class="header-stat" aria-hidden="true">
            <span class="stat-number">100+</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Events Produced</span>
          </div>
          <div class="header-stat" aria-hidden="true">
            <span class="stat-number">10+</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Years in Crypto</span>
          </div>
          <div class="header-stat" aria-hidden="true">
            <span class="stat-number">Global</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Reach</span>
          </div>
          <div class="header-stat" aria-hidden="true">
            <span class="stat-number">Since 2015</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Industry Leaders</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="container-fluid process-section">
    <div class="about-intro">
      <div class="lg-text"><span>About Us</span></div>
      <div class="normal-text">
        <p>Amplified Event Strategy has
been the go-to cryptocurrency
events agency since 2015.<br />We’ve produced 100+ crypto
events since our 2015 agency
launch. Our events speak for themselves and we work
entirely by word of mouth.<br /><br /> Weʼre known for launching influential, flagship crypto events, including the original CoinDesk
Consensus in 2015; Solana Breakpoint in 2021 2022; and most recently, the Ondo Summit in
2025.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="process-boxes">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <div class="text-box" data-number="01">
            <div class="title">Founded in Crypto</div>
            <p>We launched in 2015, the same year CoinDesk Consensus was born. We didn't enter the crypto events industry — we helped build it.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <div class="text-box" data-number="02">
            <div class="title">Full-Service Production</div>
            <p>From venue contracting and stage design to AV, catering, and signage, we manage every detail so you can stay focused on your audience.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <div class="text-box" data-number="03">
            <div class="title">Word of Mouth, By Design</div>
            <p>We don't advertise. Every client has come to us through a referral. Our track record speaks — and so do our clients.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <div class="text-box" data-number="04">
            <div class="title">Global Reach</div>
            <p>We've produced events on six continents, bringing together the world's most influential crypto founders, investors, and builders in rooms that matter.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <div class="text-box" data-number="05">
            <div class="title">High-Profile Speakers</div>
            <p>We manage speaker pipelines for the biggest names in the industry — from protocol founders to institutional investors to heads of state.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <div class="text-box" data-number="06">
            <div class="title">Flagship Events</div>
            <p>From the original Consensus in 2015 to Solana Breakpoint in 2021–2022 to the Ondo Summit in 2025, we've been behind the events that define the crypto calendar.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container-fluid team-section">
    <div class="team-section-header">
      <div class="lg-text"><span>The Amplified Team</span></div>
      <p class="team-section-blurb">We are best known for our veteran cryptocurrency and Wall Street event experts. Given our years of hands-on event experience in both the crypto and traditional financial markets sector, we specialize in events targeting developers, institutional investors, crypto enthusiasts and other Web 3 adjacent audiences.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="team-member">
      <div class="team-member-photo">
        <div class="photo-placeholder"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="team-member-info">
        <div class="team-member-name">Lauren Laino</div>
        <div class="team-member-title">Founder & CEO</div>
        <p>Lauren founded Amplified 11+ years ago and
is a former lawyer. She brings 20+ years of
conference business and Wall Street event
experience to the team. She specializes in
event strategy and large scale event
production. She helped launch the first
Consensus event in 2015 and countless major
crypto events including the Solana Breakpoint
2021 launch.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="team-member">
      <div class="team-member-photo">
        <div class="photo-placeholder"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="team-member-info">
        <div class="team-member-name">Elaine Cancelliere</div>
        <div class="team-member-title">Speaker Management Lead</div>
        <p>Elaine has worked on countless crypto events over the last 7 years,
procuring the speaker management system for large scale events
such as Solanaʼs Breakpoint, NearCon and CoinDeskʼs Consensus.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="team-member">
      <div class="team-member-photo">
        <div class="photo-placeholder"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="team-member-info">
        <div class="team-member-name">Olivia Fore</div>
        <div class="team-member-title">Sponsorship Lead</div>
        <p>Olivia has managed and produced live events over the past 12 years.
She has worked in various industries ranging from fashion and
music festivals to crypto and the cruising industry.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="team-member">
      <div class="team-member-photo">
        <div class="photo-placeholder"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="team-member-info">
        <div class="team-member-name">Trisha Gallagher</div>
        <div class="team-member-title">Production/Ops Lead</div>
        <p>Tricia has 20+ years of event production and management
experience. She leads all event ops and production including site
selections, budget management, and acts as a liaison between all
teams.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="team-member">
      <div class="team-member-photo">
        <div class="photo-placeholder"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="team-member-info">
        <div class="team-member-name">Zack Seward</div>
        <div class="team-member-title">Content Lead</div>
        <p>Zack ran CoinDeskʼs news coverage as Deputy Editor-in-Chief until
July 2022 before transitioning to conference programming. He still
appears daily as a commentator on CoinDesk TV.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="team-member">
      <div class="team-member-photo">
        <div class="photo-placeholder"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="team-member-info">
        <div class="team-member-name">Joon Ian Wong</div>
        <div class="team-member-title">Content Lead</div>
        <p>In the space since 2013, Joon started the CoinDesk Consensus
conference in 2015, expanding it globally in 2019. He co-founded the
Association of Cryptocurrency Journalists and Researchers.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container-fluid history-section">
    <div class="history-inner">
      <div class="history-header">
        <div class="lg-text"><span>A Proven History of Producing "Must-Attend" Industry Events</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="history-grid">
        <div class="history-item">
          <div class="history-year">2013</div>
          <p>Agency launched and has been a long-standing and trusted partner of top Web 3 projects while having Wall Street / institutional event background</p>
        </div>
        <div class="history-item">
          <div class="history-year">2021</div>
          <p>Launched <strong>Messari Mainnet</strong> and <strong>Solana Breakpoint</strong>, the latter with a decentralized format for 2,000 attendees and 5 venues as the first major event post-COVID</p>
        </div>
        <div class="history-item">
          <div class="history-year">2015</div>
          <p>Planned and produced the very first large scale crypto / Web3 conference - the original <strong>CoinDesk Consensus</strong> at the Times Center in NYC</p>
        </div>
        <div class="history-item">
          <div class="history-year">2025</div>
          <p>Launched the <strong>Ondo Summit</strong> in New York City - one of the most hyped events of the year - an invite-only, institutional launch event in February 2025</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container-fluid success-section">
    <div class="success-inner">
      <div class="success-header">
        <div class="lg-text"><span>Success Stories</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="success-body">
        <ul class="success-events">
          <li>Ondo Summit 2025</li>
          <li>HederaCon 2025</li>
          <li>Solana Breakpoint 2021, 2022 events</li>
          <li>Nearcon 2022, 2023, 2024 events</li>
          <li>Chainlink SmartCon 2023, 2024, 2025 events</li>
          <li>Stacks 2022, 2023, 2024, 2025 events</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="success-common">
          <p>While these events and projects are all very different vis-a-vis one another - what do these events have in common:</p>
          <ul class="success-traits">
            <li>Collaboration with our clients to understand the vibe of their project and then bring that vision to life for them!</li>
            <li>Professionally run events - seems easy to say but not as common at Web 3 events and other event producers.</li>
            <li>Clients bring us back year-after-year - we rarely work with a client just once.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="success-logos">
        <div class="logo-holder"><img src="/images/client1.png" alt="Hedera" /></div>
        <div class="logo-holder"><img src="/images/client2.png" alt="Near" /></div>
        <div class="logo-holder"><img src="/images/client3.png" alt="Ondo" /></div>
        <div class="logo-holder"><img src="/images/client4.png" alt="Solana" /></div>
        <div class="logo-holder"><img src="/images/client5.png" alt="Chainlink" /></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container-fluid other-content">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col">
        <div class="lg-text">Have a project<br />for us?</div>
        <div class="normal-text">
          <p>The world's best crypto events started with a single email.<br />Yours could be next.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="btn-holder">
          <a href="#" class="cr-btn black ex-padding">Let's talk</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
